{"tid":750383,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"呢世人都唔想再聽到麥明詩、馮盈盈既名！！！","createTime":"2018-07-20T23:18:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-28T20:28:58.000Z","uid":119450,"like":50,"dislike":87,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"72e761ffd663be6d55109357d1b2a6536e7e6100","tid":750383,"uid":119450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T23:18:59.000Z","msg":"由細到大都覺得女仔識少少淫好正<br />\n會令男人有遐想 但又未至於想J佢<br />\n可以話係兩性關係既平衡點<br />\n<br />\n依家睇到馮盈盈同麥明詩既新聞真係覺得好嘔心<br />\n簡直呢世人都唔想再聽到呢兩個嘔心女人既名<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母臭閪一日到黑講淫野上位 電視又講 訪問又講<br />\n仲要大大聲個隻 以為咁就係性格好真 男女好平等啦<br />\n但俾著係男藝人講 一早俾女權、港女話係下流賤格 性騷擾<br />\n<br />\n我話知你現實中係10A 港大 好有內涵 識陶傑好威威<br />\n冇人想知啊！講啲垃圾野污染大眾！<br />\n因為網絡上某一班嘩眾取寵既人 <br />\n而係現實中取悅佢地 又或者當成個社會都係呢班人<br />\n靠咁去谷人氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有句說話真係講得岩 人必自侮 然後人侮之<br />\n自己毀滅高尚人格 以後就冇人會再尊重你呀食屎狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77953cdcaa8d8a4a34117b546444d1ab0b75c4d6","tid":750383,"uid":555,"like":44,"dislike":1,"score":43,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T23:20:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s1.gifyu.com/images/bj05bf11ced8aa5bc7.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs1.gifyu.com%2Fimages%2Fbj05bf11ced8aa5bc7.gif&h=f7d1f001&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d3f2ca5d8bbd71f24a0682a953edda9c0dcdf0d5","tid":750383,"uid":21423,"like":26,"dislike":1,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T23:20:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5ed758221832567413472e8f8c9cc4f2eb3f448a","tid":750383,"uid":119450,"like":2,"dislike":7,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T23:21:22.000Z","msg":"Show Blocked User - 張學友ʕ≧ᴥ≦ʔ"},{"pid":"75ca6fe9488659fa5cbe24420aec407d7dc15b13","tid":750383,"uid":183691,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T23:24:52.000Z","msg":"真係講得太多 聽到悶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"180734ddb2a5e67640aff78262b8d052168110ca","tid":750383,"uid":5190,"like":3